Cape Town cops need SunReaders’ help to track down a man. “Please contact the police if you know the whereabouts of the person in the photo. The person might be able to assist in the investigation of a murder case,” said Western Cape police spokesman Captain Frederick van Wyk. Anyone with information can call Detective- Warrant Officer Shaun Bardien on 021 467 6320, 021 467 8001 and 073 220 0653 or alternatively CrimeStop on 08600 10111.